        "attack": "Aqua Jet: Fires a jet stream of water at an enemy, dealing physical Water damage.",
        "skill": "Water Sport: Drops three water geysers in a triangle, dealing physical Water damage.",
        "skill2": "Aqua Cutter: Slices an enemy with pressurized water, dealing physical Water damage. This can hit towers.",
        "ult": "Bubble Beam: Channels a wide line of bubbles, dealing physical Water damage to all enemies and towers hit.",
        "passive": "Clingy: Attaches to a nearby allied Pokemon, becoming untargetable and movement-rooted while sharing most of Clawitzer's HP and defenses. Detaches if the ally dies or takes a huge hit."
      },
      "pokemon_moba_octillery": {
