        "skill2": "Bouncy Bubble: Fires a Water bubble that lands three times along an aimed path, dealing physical damage at each impact.",
        "ult": "Octazooka: Fires a massive Water projectile in a line, dealing heavy physical damage to the first enemy hit.",
        "passive": "Suction Cups: Intended terrain-walking passive. This is pending a lower-level pathing hook."
      },
      "pokemon_moba_pyukumuku": {
        "name": "Pyukumuku",
        "attack": "Harden: Briefly ignores incoming damage, then gains increased defense.",
        "skill": "Toxic: Applies two stacks of Poison to the target.",
        "skill2": "Rest: Falls asleep, becoming unable to act while rapidly healing.",
        "ult": "Pain Split: Averages Pyukumuku's current HP with the target's current HP, then splits the total evenly between them.",
        "passive": "Innards Out: Burn and Poison heal Pyukumuku. Melee attacks against Pyukumuku reflect increasing damage from repeat attackers and may poison them. Direct damage that kills Pyukumuku is partly reflected back."
      },
