        "skill": "Shadow Sneak: Dashes through shadows to the target, dealing physical Ghost damage and forcing the target toward Banette's starting point.",
        "skill2": "Night Shade: Releases a short shadow cone, dealing physical Ghost damage and briefly blinding enemies.",
