        "skill2": "Sing: Sings a lingering song that puts nearby enemies to Sleep while they remain in the aura.",
        "ult": "Bug Buzz: Emits a damaging buzzing aura that Confuses nearby enemies.",
        "passive": "Web Walker: Sticky Webs create permanent control zones that speed Kricketune and lightly slow enemies."
      },
